                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def1-537-18570406 t18570406-537-punishment-87"></join>Confined Six Months</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="largeCaps">MORRIS</hi>—<hi rend="smallCaps">
                     <rs id="t18570406-537-verdict-2" type="verdictDescription">
